  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 13th level, you know which words to say to extinguish hostility in a person. While a creature is under the effects of a Genjutsu you cast within 30 feet of you, as an action, your words attempt to resonate in that creature as it makes a Charisma saving throw. On a failed save, it becomes non-hostile to you and all creatures you are allied with. If it takes damage from you or your allies, it becomes becomes hostile again. A creature that succeeds the saving throw is immune to this effect for the next 24 hours. This feature can be used once per long rest. At 17th level, this can be used twice per long rest.</p>",
